# NOTE: command-center/heartbeat.json IS tracked. #642 ignored it to stop
# git-log pollution but broke the deployed Command Center (Pages 404). Now
# committed via commit_heartbeat_if_due() with hybrid cadence (≥10 min or
# HEAD-moved piggyback) to keep noise low without breaking the UI.
